                            <comment id="14037909" author="yhuai" created="Thu, 19 Jun 2014 21:21:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause of this bug is that in HashJoin, outputPartitioning returns the output partitioning of its left child. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
